high_descs: Turn left, go past the fridge, turn right, go to the table across the room.
Pick up the dirty bowl with a yellow knife in it on the table.
Turn around, bring the dirty bowl to the sink on your left.
Wash the dirty bowl in the sink with water, fill the bowl with water.
Bring the filled bowl to the fridge on the right.
Put the bowl filled with water in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl filled with water in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to cross the room and face the white table.
Pick the bowl with the knife in it up from the table.
Turn around and face the sink.
Put the bowl in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the bowl back up.
Go to the right and turn to the left to face the fridge.
Put the bowl in the fridge and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bowl in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left then right to go around refrigerator, proceed to table across room.
Pick up bowl with knife in it from table.
Turn around, proceed to sink on left.  Turn left to face sink.
Place pan with knife in sink, fill pan with water.
Turn left, proceed to refrigerator on left.  Turn left to face refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, place on shelf directly above mug, close refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Fill bowl with knife with water and put in refrigerator.
